choices.text:
when President Barak Obama was elected as first African American President of state. It was not love at first sight but both Obama and US A were looking for a new, fresh way to live. In my opinion and facts, I deem 21st century is American century. In breaking history and manner US is going forward and proving that freedom is economic power. As Obama said, the time is for those who dare to change, rebel, to ask and to act. The only case when it does not work to this way around, is when you are procrastinating.

US is moving on an intricate and complex road, but each day closer to their ideals and dreams. Second president of USA had one of motto it is written on US bills „In god we trust“ which means that they trust in their work and religion.

Born is revolutionary way. Elevated in the American society, which has struggled through centuries, went through breaking and hardships, solidified and built. US followed one thing when they wrote history, Civil war, which divided nation by those who slaves and those who were free; the passing century of freedom struggle is ongoing, but this flexibility is making US a better place for all of us.

I agree with what Obama says and I do believe that everything he said will happen someday. I strongly believe that everything the presidents say while campaigning is some sort of basis and a plan to do something. But we have seen so many past presidents that promised a lot but could deliver anything.
